{"tid":1290041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[嚴正呼籲]CCTVB係永遠嘅敵人","createTime":"2019-07-06T10:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:50:48.000Z","uid":22047,"like":93,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc3c718d92a0a5a0424e90b1438bea77a8d8c60","tid":1290041,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個唔撚係分化POST</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有好多連登仔見CCTVB出條女就即刻動搖，請認清事實：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB做嘅陰質野足以影響幾代香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例：暗角七警係CCTVB拍低，唔通CCTVB新聞部就唔係仆街？<br />\n<br />\n條女可以自己嘅立場，東張西望都可以有佢嘅立場，<span style=\"color: red;\">但當時佢係代表緊CCTVB</span><br />\n<br />\n佢有權唔做CCTVB，佢亦都有權利係唔係工作嘅時候發表意見<br />\n<br />\n警告：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認真身份最重要，切勿精蟲上腦</span></span>"},{"pid":"3937886b3117521f47a9842e4fd2caef23da3f8b","tid":1290041,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3abfc53d15cc379716049cdd0c7b2121186ca8","tid":1290041,"uid":205339,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"大家有無聽過good cop bad cop<br />\n唔好中計啊！！<br />\n<br />\n恥與為伍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：丁開wingto"},{"pid":"a20e2c0bc28c8d2f8b6455b47acd82db2621935a","tid":1290041,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4169a50dc86504f1b095e8581b45a6ced928b65d","tid":1290041,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e32e9a